## 洞察力observant: fact and opinion(2017-07-13)

插卡后free无内存
free + mount + free 后确定是 mount 消耗
使用 exFat 格式化 64G sdcard 后 mount 不会有这个问题

事件的层次：
  插卡后free无内存，只是表象。
  mount是应用层能跟踪到的最后线索。

事件的因素：
  sdcard(Kingston, samsung)
  Capacity(8G, 16G, 32G)
  FS(fat32, exFat, NTFS)
  Kernel

解决方案：
  能量守恒，最终是需要用差异化(概念=属+种差)，change often 来进行改进，改善。

  make menuconfig
    /cache
    /mmc

  mount.fat32 usefree
    Use the "free clusters" value stored on FSINFO. It'll be used to determine number of free clusters without scanning disk. 
    But it's not used  by  default,  because recent Windows don't update it correctly in some case. 
    If you are sure the "free clusters" on FSINFO is correct, by this option you can avoid scanning disk.


